author: wsjcom
title: What’s the Deal
text:
GARMENT DISTRICT A Digital Tenant for 1001 Sixth Ave. A revamped former manufacturing and showroom building in Manhattan’s Garment District is adding a digital tenant.
The Social Edge, a social-media marketing and content-management firm, has signed a lease to take about 12,000 square feet of space on the 14th floor of 1001 Ave. of the Americas, said Jay Caseley, executive managing director of ABS Partners Real Estate LLC.
